*Autobus* je stigao u grad. (The bus has arrived to the city.)

Putnici su čekali *autobus*. (The passengers were waiting for the bus.)

Vozač *autobusa* je bio premoren. (The bus driver was exhausted.)

*Autobusom* se može stići do aerodroma. (You can get to the airport by bus.)

U *autobusu* je bilo mnogo ljudi. (There were many people in the bus.)